description: MeTA is a workflow implemented to minimize microstructural heterogeneity in diffusion MRI (dMRI) metrics by extracting and parcellating the core volume along the bundle length in the voxel-space directly while effectively preserving bundle shape and efficiently capturing the regional variation within and along white matter (WM) bundles.
name: meta-neuro
